OL,3,CTeachers consulted on 2.8% pay rise
OL,4,Cand potential strike action
OL,6,FTeachers are to be consulted about a
OL,7,F2.8% pay rise and whether they are
OL,8,Fprepared to strike over the offer.
OL,10,FAround 284,000 members of the National
OL,11,FEducation Union (NEU) working in
OL,12,Fmaintained schools in England will be
OL,13,Fasked to vote on accepting or
OL,14,Frejecting the Government's
OL,15,Frecommendation and if they want to
OL,16,Ftake industrial action.
